  "original_title": "\u0d9a\u0daf\u0dd2\u0dbb\u0dcf \u0d85\u0dad\u0dca\u0d85\u0da9\u0d82\u0d9c\u0dd4\u0dc0\u0da7",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Kadira arrested",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Police Special Task Force says that the main shooter of Harak Kata, an organized criminal and drug trafficker who was arrested in Dubai, was arrested while staying at a boarding house on Malani Bulathsinghala Mawatha, Boralasgamuwa.",
        "Police say that the arrested person is Prabodha Kumara alias Kadira, 28, a resident of Weligama, Midigama.",
        "Police have taken 4 live bullets used for T-56 firearms and 17 grams of stolen drugs in the suspect's possession.",
        "The suspect was arrested based on information received by the officers of the Special Task Force Organized Crime Unit 2.",
        "On the fifth day of April by the suspect. In Weligama area, Chuti Mama was shot and injured in both legs and on May 14, Roshan alias Jacka was shot and seriously injured. A police officer said that apart from rape and robbery, he was also wanted for a number of robberies.",
        "One and a half months ago, the suspect had taken the boarding house at Malani Bulathsinghala Mawatha, Boralasgamuwa for three months on the basis of monthly rent of 6000 rupees and the owner of the boarding house said that she was given an amount of 18,000 rupees for that.",
        "She said that the suspect Kadira said that he was working as a titanium floor tiler and showed a photo of a woman who claimed to be his wife and a photo of a child. The owner added that a copy of the national identity card was obtained and he was accommodated.",
        "The suspect has been handed over to the Matara Division Crime Squad for further investigation."
      ],
